data.description: Welcome to this charming detached single-family home in the heart of Collingswood Borough! This well-maintained property is the epitome of comfort and convenience. With three spacious bedrooms, this home offers plenty of room for a growing family or those seeking extra space for guests or a home office.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room boasts ample natural light, providing a cozy space for relaxation and entertainment. The adjacent dining room is perfect for gatherings and hosting dinner parties.  The kitchen is a delightful blend of modern functionality and classic design. It features well-kept appliances, countertops, and plenty of cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze. The breakfast nook is a fantastic spot to enjoy your morning coffee while overlooking the beautiful backyard.  The three bedrooms are generously sized and offer great versatility for various needs.   Step outside to discover the wonderful backyard, perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or just unwinding on the patio. The detached garage provides additional storage and additional parking.  Collingswood Borough is a sought-after community known for its charming streets and vibrant local culture. This home is conveniently located within walking distance to shops, restaurants, and public transportation, making it a prime choice for those who value convenience and lifestyle.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely Collingswood home your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and potential this property has to offer. It's a true gem in an ideal location.  Contact us to arrange your private tour and explore the possibilities of calling this delightful property your new home.
